      <div class="negative block"></div>
      <div class="actualresult">
        <div class="negative sentence">Thanks to Obamacare, I had the knee surgery I needed.</div>
        <div class="article"><a class="articlelink" href="http://www.google.com">Nobody Benefits from Obamacare? Think Again.</a> &mdash; Dan Brown</div>
      </div>
    </div>
